title: Wretched Mess Calendar 1979.cbz
description: The Wretched Mess News was a counter-culture (druggie/hippie) type of publication originating from West Yellowstone, Montana.  They also issued an annual (what other kind is there?) calendar from (at least) the years 1972 through 1979 (as far as I can tell).  I remember my brother having one of these calendars when I was about 10 years old and thought it was the most hilarious thing ever.  I am still looking for a copy of the one that he used to have, I think it was 1975. Anyway, for those interested in a look back at the 70s (and who isn't), here is a tiny glimpse of what was going on.  At least in Montana.
